    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Alternative Cost: 6 Light</p><p>Your Sharingan amplifies your already exceptional physical abilities to compensate for its otherworldly perceptive capabilities.</p><p>You move with such speed that you instantly appear into a space up to four times your movement speed in distance. All creatures of your choice within 5 feet of you when you end this movement become targets for your flurry of strikes. Make 3 melee Mangekyō Art Attacks. On a hit you deal your unarmed (or Weapon) damage + 6d6 and the target creatures gain 1 rank of slow for each successful hit you make.</p>",
